[37.225521, "o", "All four artifacts updated and both tracker issues created:\r\n\r\n**Docs updated:**\r\n- `prd.md` — added P0-4 (C→K) and P0-5 (K→C)\r\n- `FEAT-001-temperature-conversion.md` — added FR-5/FR-6 and two acceptance criteria (`--to-kelvin 100 → 373.1`, `--from-kelvin 273.15 → 0.0`)\r\n- `TD-001-temperature-conversion.md` — added `toKelvin(c)` / `fromKelvin(k)` exports, K formula, and `--to-kelvin` / `--from-kelvin` flags\r\n\r\n**Tracker issues created:**\r\n- `temp-converter-7719ee1f` — Add failing tests for Kelvin conversion (FEAT-001)\r\n- `temp-converter-5dfcb92b` — Implement Kelvin conversion in bin/convert.js (TD-001)\r\n\r\n"]
